reviewText: Not enough of the Big Four of the original Strapped Crew, imo.  Fun to watch, but I think it's misleading to list Laird Hamilton as being featured.  I guess it is (was?) his production company?  I would've liked to see more of Hamilton, Doerner, Kerbox, Kalama- but I guess I'll have to watch Riding Giants ANOTOTHER 1oo times for that. :)
